title: Quick Take: Iowa Caucus Results
description: The 2016 Iowa caucuses are history. Now what? This episode: congressional reporter Ailsa Chang, campaign reporter Asma Khalid, editor and correspondent Ron Elving, and national political correspondent Don Gonyea. Find the team on Twitter @ailsachang, @asmamk, @NPRrelving, @DonGonyea, or at npr.org/politics — and email the show at nprpolitics@npr.org.
